<fib label="Q1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Enter your e-mail address so we can contact you if you are a winner: </font><blank label="a" length="40" required="true" alternateLabel="email"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q2"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Enter a name that your team will be known by on the Leaderboard. Unless you are adding to your existing teams, be sure to use the same team name in this stage as in previous stages.: </font><blank label="a" length="40" required="false" alternateLabel="tname"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">You start by selecting one center (C), one power forward (PF), one small forward (SF), one shooting guard (SG) and one point guard (PG) to comprise your starting lineup. You are not limited to position for your other three selections. </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><b>If you make your first five selections and get sent back to this spot, it means that you have two or more players at one position and none at another position. Review your entry and make the appropriate adjustments.</b></font></paragraph></text>
